com.launchdarkly.sdk.server.interfaces

Class DataStoreTypes

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.launchdarkly.sdk.server.interfaces.DataStoreTypes

  • public abstract class DataStoreTypes
extends java.lang.Object
    Types that are used by the DataStore interface.

    Applications should never need to use any of these types unless they are implementing a custom data store.

    5.0.0
